::: {#17f11490 .cell execution_count=1}
``` {.python .cell-code}
from bertopic import BERTopic
from sklearn.datasets import fetch_20newsgroups
from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer
```
:::


::: {#9ff5e1bd .cell execution_count=2}
``` {.python .cell-code}
docs = fetch_20newsgroups(subset='all',  remove=('headers', 'footers', 'quotes'))['data']
```
:::


::: {#92778687 .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# 384-dimensional sentence embeddings (cf. GPT davinci with 12K+)

embedding_model = SentenceTransformer("all-MiniLM-L6-v2", device="mps")

# if NOT on Apple Silicon device, use rather
# embedding_model = SentenceTransformer("all-MiniLM-L6-v2")
```
:::


::: {#f6132d07 .cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
embeddings = embedding_model.encode(docs, show_progress_bar=True)
```

